Interface TerrainHeightGenerator

All Known Implementing Classes:
SmoothedDataHistogramGenerator, UMatrixGenerator
public interface TerrainHeightGenerator

Interface for classes generating terrain topologies from SOMs. Some methods in this interface are the same as in BackgroundImageVisualizer.
